{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/journal/2020/02/five-things","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"41d0c7ae-91ae-5e8e-9b6f-b192a6dc300a","html":"<p>I’ve wanted to get back in to blogging for a while; partly to brush up on my writing skills and partly to get some sort of recent online presence again. I’ve found my use of Twitter dwindle, but perhaps posting these posts up there will engage my followers?</p>\n<p>For the next few weeks I’m going to make posts with five things I’ve found interesting/good/useful.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-parasite\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-parasite\" aria-label=\"1 parasite permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. <a href=\"https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6751668/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Parasite</a></h2>\n<p>This year, for the first time, I’ve managed to see all the nominees for Best Picture at the Oscars.\nParasite was definitely up there with the best; I also really enjoyed 1917. My least favourite was Joker, which I just couldn’t get behind. Parasite was a great combination of comedy and tragedy.\nSee Mark Kermode’s <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/feb/09/parasite-review-bong-joon-ho-tragicomic-masterpiece\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">review over at The Guardian</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-pollen-bakery\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-pollen-bakery\" aria-label=\"2 pollen bakery permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. <a href=\"http://pollenbakery.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Pollen Bakery</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 567px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/a7172/1-pollen.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/8ac56/1-pollen.webp 240w,\n/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/d3be9/1-pollen.webp 480w,\n/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/66779/1-pollen.webp 567w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/09b79/1-pollen.jpg 240w,\n/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/7cc5e/1-pollen.jpg 480w,\n/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/a7172/1-pollen.jpg 567w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/b7c3aa62af84b8dba302482c83272b3d/a7172/1-pollen.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Pollen Shakshuka and Tahini pastry\"\n          title=\"Pollen Shakshuka and Tahini pastry\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\nAnyone who has visited me in Manchester will have been dragged to Pollen at some point.\nIt’s my favourite bakery, making everything with sourdough (yes, even the pastry). It sates my desire for Danish pastry (or wienerbrød as it is known in Denmark) and they even sell Danish style rye bread.\nI’ve scaled back my home baking recently, but it’s always a treat to head to Pollen for some brunch and have a chat with them about different flours and styles of bread. (I do miss the time when they were based in a railway arch and I would regularly queue for half an hour on Saturday morning to get the elusive Cruffin).</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-acm-membership\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-acm-membership\" aria-label=\"3 acm membership permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. <a href=\"https://www.acm.org/membership\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ACM Membership</a></h2>\n<p>For a while I kept acquiring dead-tree programming books, many of which I only gave a cursory read.\nI eventually joined O’Reilly Safari on one of their big discounts. I heard later (<a href=\"https://twitter.com/martinkl/status/1083324384947945474?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">via Martin Kleppman</a>) that if you join the Association of Computing Machinery, you also have access to Safari.\nI’ve been a member ever since, and while I still don’t have the patience to read many books cover to cover, it feels like the best tech library I could wish for.\nACM Membership is $100, quite a discount over Safari. </p>\n<h2 id=\"4-go-time-cloudy-with-a-chance-of-kelsey-hightower\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-go-time-cloudy-with-a-chance-of-kelsey-hightower\" aria-label=\"4 go time cloudy with a chance of kelsey hightower permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. <a href=\"https://changelog.com/gotime/114\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Go Time: Cloudy with a chance of Kelsey Hightower</a></h2>\n<p>This podcast episode was informative and entertaining (Kelsey usually is worth paying attention to).\nIn particular, I enjoyed his rant about microservices. They have exploded in popularity over the past 5 years, but as he <a href=\"https://changelog.com/gotime/114#transcript-96\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">describes here</a> I’m not convinced we should give up on well-crafted monoliths.</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-aldis-organic-apple-cider-vinegar\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-aldis-organic-apple-cider-vinegar\" aria-label=\"5 aldis organic apple cider vinegar permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Aldi’s Organic Apple Cider Vinegar</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 567px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/8ac56/1-aldi-acv.webp 240w,\n/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/d3be9/1-aldi-acv.webp 480w,\n/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/66779/1-aldi-acv.webp 567w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/09b79/1-aldi-acv.jpg 240w,\n/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/7cc5e/1-aldi-acv.jpg 480w,\n/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/a7172/1-aldi-acv.jpg 567w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/5a71465f61670e00a10cf0ee941bb4b9/a7172/1-aldi-acv.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Aldi Organic Apple Cider Vinegar\"\n          title=\"Aldi Organic Apple Cider Vinegar\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span>\nI don’t want these posts to become an ad for Aldi, but I think it’s worth pointing out a good product when I find one.\nThis week’s is their organic unfiltered cider vinegar. I’ve started making a drink with a teaspoon of this, a teaspoon of lemon juice and cold water. It’s a refreshing way to start the day, and apparently has <a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/6-proven-health-benefits-of-apple-cider-vinegar#section4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">many health benefits</a> too.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/journal/2020/02/five-things","tagSlugs":null},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-20T22:33:25.000Z","description":"A return to blogging.","tags":null,"title":"Five things - 20/02/2020","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/journal/2020/02/five-things"}}}